ediate valency-specified enumerators (both for undirected and directed\ncirculant graphs) and their validity is conjectured for arbitrary cubed odd\nprime $p^3$.\n  We believe that this research can serve as the crucial step towards explicit\nuniform enumeration formulae for circulant graphs of orders $p^3$ for arbitrary\nprime $p>2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Dec 2015 08:09:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Mar 2017 08:36:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 6 Apr 2018 10:08:00 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 9 Apr 2018 16:48:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-10"}
