re than chiral order becomes ubiquitous\ndeparting from high point group symmetry chiral building blocks, such as $I$,\n$O$ and $T$ symmetric matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Dec 2015 14:20:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Dec 2015 21:32:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 25 Feb 2016 19:48:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2016 15:39:44 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 31 Oct 2016 19:32:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-01"}
